nodes.text: Commenor brandy was a type of brandy from the planet Commenor. First produced well before the Great Galactic War between the Galactic Republic and the Sith Empire, Commenor brandy was known for its quality and semi-addictive reputation.
Commenor brandy was first mentioned in the 2012 reference guide Star Wars: The Old Republic Encyclopedia's entry for Bevera Dodonna.
